Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{=4}---- Dialogue
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.37,0:00:12.74,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki{**-san}...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.59,0:00:24.96,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Get your filthy hands...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.55,0:00:27.09,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,off of Atri!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.93,0:00:31.05,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Stand down.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.73,0:00:42.02,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,So you side with the Humanoid, do you?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.52,0:00:44.90,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri has a heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.23,0:00:47.53,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Just like any one of us!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.37,0:00:54.24,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.58,0:00:59.16,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki{**-san}...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.67,0:01:01.67,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.58,0:01:06.17,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,What a truly wretched machine you are,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.17,0:01:09.17,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,deceiving this poor boy to such an extent.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.72,0:01:13.43,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.14,0:01:17.93,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Professor Konishi was truly
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.39,0:01:21.27,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,a sinful man.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.27,0:01:28.40,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Nothing short of the devil\ncould have ever wrought such a creation.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.16,0:01:35.70,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,For you see...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.70,0:01:40.87,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,if this unit hadn't committed that atrocity,\nif it hadn't escaped justice,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.87,0:01:43.75,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,both the professor and the factory\nwould be alive and well.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.29,0:01:48.71,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,But all because of this {\i1}thing{\i0},\nthis defective pile of scrap metal...{wtf, where's the whistle-blowing _now_? -p}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.13,0:01:50.97,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.13,0:01:56.05,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,A-Atri isn't...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.55,0:01:59.97,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri isn't defective...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.23,0:02:02.60,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,You're a lost cause, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.60,0:02:04.06,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.65,0:02:09.32,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki{**-san} has nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.86,0:02:14.11,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Then what do you propose?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.96,0:03:52.30,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,{\an8}Then what do you propose?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.77,0:04:15.11,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,Did you see that, friends?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.11,0:04:17.11,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,That was a clear act of violence!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.11,0:04:21.12,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,This Humanoid, in contravention\nof the Three Laws, struck me!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.12,0:04:26.79,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,This lowly manmade {\i1}tool{\i0} struck a {\i1}human!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.66,0:04:30.33,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,And so the truth comes out!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.33,0:04:32.54,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,This is more than I had even hoped for!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.88,0:04:35.30,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,A robot has harmed a human!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.71,0:04:38.09,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,The proof is incontrovertible!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.09,0:04:39.93,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,This unit is defective!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.43,0:04:44.18,Default,Yasuda,0,0,0,,It cannot be allowed to roam free!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.40,Default,Subordinate A,0,0,0,,Y-Yasuda{**-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.53,0:05:01.57,Default,Subordinate A,0,0,0,,S-Stay back!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.59,0:05:16.67,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.55,0:05:21.93,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki{**-san}...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.72,0:05:28.22,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Please decommission me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.93,0:05:30.81,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.98,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm defective.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.35,0:05:36.86,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm willing to hurt and injure people.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.86,0:05:38.86,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm a defective Humanoid.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.16,0:05:45.91,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You have to destroy me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.38,0:05:56.25,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Atri.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.59,0:06:01.05,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I said all those horrible things to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.26,0:06:06.05,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I just had to apologize,\neven if it meant running all the way here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.39,0:06:10.89,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I was so,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.73,0:06:14.56,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,so terrible to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.15,0:06:18.23,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.28,0:06:21.28,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,If anyone's defective, it's me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.28,0:06:23.11,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,D-Don't say that!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.61,0:06:26.24,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You have nothing to apologize for...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.08,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.66,0:06:32.58,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.71,0:06:36.38,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You {\i1}do{\i0} have a heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.00,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It was just a glitch.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.25,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Not a heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.13,0:06:44.97,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I... have nothing of the sort.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.97,0:06:46.26,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.18,0:06:49.76,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,How are you supposed to know that for sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.26,0:06:53.06,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Nobody knows what the heart is.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.27,0:06:57.73,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Heck, I don't know the first thing about mine,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.73,0:07:01.03,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,or if I even have one at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.53,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's how it is to be human.{he's only human, after all; don't put the blame on him -p}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.54,0:07:15.16,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What are you feeling now?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.50,0:07:17.92,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.92,0:07:19.50,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You don't have to hold back.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.42,0:07:22.17,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You don't have to keep it bottled up.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.05,0:07:24.92,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Just let the emotions wash over you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.60,0:07:30.97,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You remember now, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.64,0:07:37.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.35,0:08:14.93,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,She's crying...{Okay, I'll be honest. I wasn't expecting this to rattle me as much as it did.}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.08,0:08:38.62,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Shiina...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.62,0:08:42.33,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,That's her first master's name?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.84,0:08:43.63,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.42,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,My mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.05,0:08:48.63,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Ah, makes sense.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.63,0:08:51.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That explains why you found her\nwith your grandma's stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.14,0:08:57.52,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Oh, look...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.81,0:09:00.14,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah. Those are tear stains.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.14,0:09:01.31,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.81,0:09:05.98,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri was crying,\nand she didn't even notice it herself.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.98,0:09:08.99,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,But I thought she said she couldn't cry...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.99,0:09:13.66,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She just assumed that Humanoids could never cry.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.66,0:09:15.37,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That she couldn't shed any tears.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.37,0:09:18.66,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Because she had no heart, no real emotions...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.21,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.21,0:09:23.67,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But those tear stains were all the proof I needed.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.13,0:09:26.17,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That she {\i1}does{\i0} have a heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.34,0:09:31.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She's been suffering\nfrom the moment she was born.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.64,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Struggling to do the things she knew were right...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.64,0:09:38.02,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She knew what she was doing was wrong,\nbut couldn't stop herself.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.02,0:09:41.85,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She's been pulled apart by all these\ncontradictory impulses from her heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.36,0:09:46.69,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.69,0:09:47.82,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki{**-san}...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.03,0:09:51.95,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Is your arm okay? Try and see if you can move it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.95,0:09:52.78,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.03,0:09:58.62,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Everything seems to be in order.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.62,0:10:00.29,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Phew, that's good.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.33,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.33,0:10:06.84,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about Yasuda ever again.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.84,0:10:10.38,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Catherine and Ryuuji are heading to\nthe mainland to talk to the police.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.76,0:10:14.05,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,We can't get him for violence against a Humanoid,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.05,0:10:18.85,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,but they did take the kids hostage\nand threaten Ryuuji with a gun.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.27,0:10:22.10,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.73,0:10:24.06,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Atri{**-chan}...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.56,0:10:26.56,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,You don't gotta worry about us!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.56,0:10:28.90,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,If anything, it felt great seeing you give it to 'em!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.40,0:10:30.82,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But still...
Comment: 10,0:10:31.61,0:10:32.70,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,[traumatized robot noises]
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.87,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Everyone makes mistakes.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.45,0:10:45.00,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,We all do things we know are wrong,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.62,0:10:48.46,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,or say things we don't really mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.88,0:10:54.22,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But because of that, we get to feel emotions\nlike joy, or sorrow, or anger.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.22,0:10:59.51,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,And right now, I feel like\nI want to always be there for you,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.51,0:11:00.60,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,because...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.06,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.48,0:11:06.10,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki{**-san}...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.23,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Those are the feelings from my heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.23,0:11:09.61,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You can tell, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.44,0:11:11.53,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.03,0:11:17.03,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,The key is to keep control over your own heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.03,0:11:19.20,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Not the other way around.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.78,0:11:22.08,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But that's something you can figure out as you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.37,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.37,0:11:26.42,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Plenty of {\i1}humans{\i0} need\ntons of practice to get good at it too!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.79,0:11:27.58,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.75,0:11:32.67,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,There might be people who doubt you\nbecause you're a Humanoid,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.67,0:11:35.05,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,but I promise I'll always be there for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.26,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.35,0:11:42.26,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.26,0:11:45.64,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,For some reason,\nI have this incredible urge to hug you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.94,0:11:50.27,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,May I?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.57,0:11:53.03,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.16,0:12:00.62,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Am I doing something wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.16,0:12:02.79,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.12,0:12:05.79,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But that's how it always is with the heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.25,0:12:11.46,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Think we should make like some trees?{is the "and leave" part even necessary, if we're gonna go with such an ESL unfriendly idiom? xD}{! -p}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.09,0:12:14.30,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I don't think it's like {\i1}that.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.30,0:12:14.96,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.96,0:12:18.34,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Their bond is something else.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.64,0:12:20.80,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Something much deeper.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.68,0:12:25.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.52,0:12:28.64,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hey, Atri?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.19,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Maybe she's tired?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.73,0:12:35.28,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Well, she was definitely consuming\na lot more power than normal.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.28,0:12:36.82,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,She was?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.24,0:12:44.87,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I think she was reading her logs\nbefore she went to school yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.87,0:12:47.62,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She was reflecting on her past,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.62,0:12:49.67,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,all the things that made her who she is,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.33,0:12:54.84,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,and that caused all her memories\nto come flooding back.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.84,0:12:57.13,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,A whole lifetime of joy and sorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.51,0:12:59.22,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hitting her all at once.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.22,0:13:01.59,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Shiina{*Shiina-sama}...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.85,0:13:07.18,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}Initializing visual sensors.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.18,0:13:09.10,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}Awaiting instructions from new owner.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.56,0:13:11.65,Default,Nonko,0,0,0,,I'm a busy woman.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.65,0:13:14.82,Default,Nonko,0,0,0,,Take care of this girl for me, got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.82,0:13:18.49,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Wow! You're the Humanoid?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.49,0:13:19.82,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.82,0:13:21.99,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Let's be friends!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.20,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,A pleasure to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.49,0:13:27.24,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,My name's Shiina. What's yours?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.24,0:13:29.83,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I do not have one. Call me whatever you wish.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.83,0:13:32.17,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,I get to name you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.17,0:13:34.21,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Um, let's see!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.21,0:13:37.21,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Ruri... Natsumi...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.21,0:13:39.38,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Oh, I know! Betty Beep-Boop!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.38,0:13:42.34,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,"Betty Beep-Boop" is a derogatory slur.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.34,0:13:45.10,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Aw, but it's so cute...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.10,0:13:47.64,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Uh, hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.23,0:13:52.35,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Atri.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.73,0:13:57.90,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,That little birdie is called an "atori."{literally just "a bird" lmao -p}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.86,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,So you can be Atri!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.82,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Whaddya think? It's a pretty name, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.53,0:14:04.91,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Atri...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.83,0:14:10.95,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was the name I was given.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.17,0:14:18.67,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Atri."
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.67,0:14:20.76,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}Under my newfound name,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.26,0:14:24.01,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}I began to live with {*}Miss Shiina{*Shiina-sama}.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.76,0:14:26.01,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.47,0:14:28.47,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.64,0:14:32.35,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Shiina{*Shiina-sama}...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.81,0:14:35.69,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,You'll get the hang of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.69,0:14:37.52,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,You're high-spec.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.86,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,High-spec?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.11,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.11,0:14:45.86,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Mom told me you were\nthe most high-spec flagship model.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.86,0:14:47.87,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,And so I'd be in good hands.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.87,0:14:49.33,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.33,0:14:53.87,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Mom always says that words have special power.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.16,0:14:59.38,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,So you should always say nice things\nand avoid saying bad things.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.96,0:15:05.63,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Why don't you try saying it for yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.22,0:15:09.01,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Go, "I'm high-spec!"
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.39,0:15:12.85,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm high-spec.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.85,0:15:14.77,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Yeah! One more time!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.77,0:15:16.56,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm high-spec!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.56,0:15:17.52,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.94,0:15:24.44,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm high-spec, baby!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.32,0:15:30.66,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}Life with {*}Miss Shiina{*Shiina-sama} was almost always\nspent with just the two of us.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.79,0:15:35.29,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Aw, can't you let me win even once?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.29,0:15:39.00,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Why are you so frightened by this particular insect?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.00,0:15:40.92,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Just kill it already!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.59,0:15:45.09,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Why go to the effort of making this?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.09,0:15:46.93,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It'd be more efficient to simply buy one.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.93,0:15:50.47,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,No, no, baking it together\nmakes for a better memory!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.14,0:15:55.10,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}But she seems as content as ever.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.10,0:15:56.44,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}All is well.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.65,0:16:02.48,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today is {*}Miss Shiina{*Shiina-sama}'s first day of middle school.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.90,0:16:05.86,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've discerned several changes\nin her affect as a result.{congrats you've made me google a word -p}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.57,0:16:08.16,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,What do you think, Atri?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.74,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,How do I look?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.03,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Very stylish.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.03,0:16:13.58,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But according to this photo,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.58,0:16:16.00,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,everyone wears the same uniform.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.00,0:16:19.75,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I worry whether I'll be able to\npick you out from the crowd.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.34,0:16:26.01,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Then if we ever can't find each other,\nhow about we sing our song?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.01,0:16:29.01,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Still remember those lyrics I taught you?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.14,0:16:38.69,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I sit on the sill to feel the rain.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.69,0:16:40.65,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.65,0:16:42.11,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.65,0:16:45.86,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,I've grown just as tall as you, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.07,0:16:48.36,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You have.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.82,0:16:53.99,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,I guess I'm gonna have to be\nthe big sister from now on...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.04,0:17:02.50,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was the very last time\nI saw {*}Miss Shiina{*Shiina-sama} smile.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.46,0:17:13.22,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}According to the report filed by the school,\nthe inciting incident was a trivial matter.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.68,0:17:18.27,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}{*}Miss Shiina{*Shiina-sama} reproached another girl\nfor talking during class.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.27,0:17:22.02,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}Presumably, the girl in question\nnursed a grudge over this interaction.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.69,0:17:24.86,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wielding the influence she held within her class,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.86,0:17:30.65,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}the girl in question incited many other students\nto become complicit in her vendetta.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.99,0:17:36.08,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}Such a case of peer abuse is\na common social issue known as "bullying."
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.08,0:17:39.00,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,I told you not to touch it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.54,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.29,0:17:46.42,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.05,0:17:51.05,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}Clear signs of elevated stress observed.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.34,0:17:55.76,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}For three concurrent months now,\nher stress levels have remained in the red zone.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.27,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}Immediate intervention is needed.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.44,0:18:04.27,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.27,0:18:06.73,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You should talk to Nonko.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.73,0:18:09.28,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Mom's busy.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.28,0:18:10.49,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.49,0:18:13.28,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,She says sea levels\nare gonna start rising any day now,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.28,0:18:16.28,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,and humanity's in for a huge crisis.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.28,0:18:19.33,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Not that anyone in her lab actually believes her.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.33,0:18:22.08,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Mom's lost her marbles, I swear...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.42,0:18:24.71,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Please take that back.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.25,0:18:28.96,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Words have power.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.80,0:18:30.46,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,If you don't mean—
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.46,0:18:32.13,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.30,0:18:37.10,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,All you do is sit around\nand stare at the wall all day,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.10,0:18:39.31,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,so don't act like you understand anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.35,0:18:42.06,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.06,0:18:46.10,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Don't you have any idea how I've been feeling?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.65,0:18:50.44,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Oh, who am I kidding?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.44,0:18:52.03,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,You're a Humanoid.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.03,0:18:54.24,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,You don't even {\i1}have{\i0} feelings.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.28,0:18:56.24,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.53,0:18:59.99,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stress levels have been further exacerbated.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.99,0:19:02.00,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}This cannot be allowed to continue.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.45,0:19:04.21,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to do something.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.58,0:19:08.21,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.05,0:19:21.81,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her class appears to have decided on the lead actress\nfor its cultural festival performance.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.10,0:19:30.11,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inferring that she was nominated\nfor the role against her will.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.94,0:19:35.95,Default,Female student D,0,0,0,,I heard she's about to jump!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.95,0:19:39.03,Default,Female Student E,0,0,0,,For real? That's so wild!{bruh fr ong? no cap? -p}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.55,0:19:58.22,Default,Teacher A,0,0,0,,Don't do anything rash!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.22,0:20:01.18,Default,Teacher B,0,0,0,,Hear us out, Yachigusa{**-san}! Let's all calm down!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.18,0:20:03.60,Default,Female Student A,0,0,0,,We all know you don't have the guts.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.68,0:20:05.64,Default,Teacher A,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.64,0:20:08.02,Default,Female Student A,0,0,0,,If you really wanna die,\nno one's gonna stop you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.02,0:20:11.36,Default,Female Student A,0,0,0,,And you won't have to act in the play that way.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.36,0:20:13.86,Default,Female Student A,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for? Jump.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.86,0:20:15.40,Default,Female Student A,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.40,0:20:26.41,Default,Female Student A; B and C,0,0,0,,{\an8}Do it! Do it! Do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.07,0:20:21.66,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}A fall from that height\nhas a fatality rate of 97 percent.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.24,0:20:23.41,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\i1}Danger.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.41,0:20:24.95,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\i1}Danger.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.41,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\i1}Danger!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.21,0:20:28.92,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must take action.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.92,0:20:29.71,Default,Female Student A,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.88,0:20:35.26,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next thing I knew...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.57,0:20:54.02,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Shii—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.90,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,Did I ever ask you to do something like this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.44,0:20:57.53,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Shiina{*Shiina-sama}—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.16,0:21:05.24,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.29,0:21:08.62,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,monster.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.42,0:21:17.05,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,I... I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.59,0:21:22.01,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But in spite of all that,\nAtri never stopped loving Shiina.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.72,0:21:26.31,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She wanted to be of use to her.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.60,0:21:31.31,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Is that why she escaped when they took her away?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.73,0:21:32.98,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Must be.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.98,0:21:35.32,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,And for years, she followed Mom in secret,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.61,0:21:37.32,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,always watching over her.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.65,0:21:49.16,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I sit on the sill... to feel the rain...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.83,0:21:56.34,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Even after Mom graduated,\ngot married, and had me...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.50,0:21:58.55,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri was always...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.80,0:22:01.88,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,always...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.72,0:22:03.93,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,always...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.59,0:22:05.85,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,right there beside her.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.47,0:22:10.14,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,And I'm guessing Grandma eventually caught her,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.73,0:22:12.98,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,wiped her memories,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.77,0:22:15.90,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,and put her to sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.73,0:22:21.40,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki{**-san}...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.40,0:22:22.95,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.66,0:22:26.53,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I had a dream.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.37,0:22:28.87,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Whew...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.87,0:22:32.37,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Um, may I ask you something?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:42.88,0:22:46.34,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I thought it'd look pretty different by now,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:46.34,0:22:48.64,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,but it hasn't changed one bit, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.10,0:22:52.39,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,That's the spot I was always watching you from.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:53.02,0:22:54.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:55.44,0:23:00.65,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Back then, I was contemplating ending\nall my vital functions right here, in this spot.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:01.19,0:23:03.19,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Just like you were.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.49,0:23:09.28,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,After all, I'd failed to save {*}Miss Shiina{*Shiina-sama},\nthe person I loved more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:11.12,0:23:12.00,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.91,0:23:17.96,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I just couldn't stand seeing you\nlook so sad, never once smiling... {?! possibly too treacherous}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.96,0:23:24.84,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,So I recalled the song and the words\n{*}Miss Shiina{*Shiina-sama} taught me all those years ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:24.84,0:23:26.30,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.30,0:23:27.84,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It'll be all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.10,0:23:32.18,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I never did thank you for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.18,0:23:32.89,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:34.35,0:23:38.10,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'm sure Mom would be really grateful, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:39.02,0:23:40.86,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:41.19,0:23:42.48,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.48,0:23:44.86,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She was always talking about this friend of hers,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:45.70,0:23:48.32,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,someone she never got the chance to apologize to.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:50.95,0:23:53.24,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,She was my very best friend.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:53.24,0:23:55.62,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,I loved her more than anyone in the whole world,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:55.62,0:23:58.25,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,but I said some horrible things I didn't mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:58.75,0:24:01.09,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,And I'm sure that really hurt her.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:04.80,0:24:07.30,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,If only I could see her one last time.
Comment: 10,0:24:08.72,0:24:09.93,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,I miss her so much.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:08.72,0:24:10.72,Default,Shiina,0,0,0,,I miss her so much.
